WEBVTT

00:03:31.793 --> 00:03:43.376
"Golden dreams
and great heartache,"

00:03:45.793 --> 00:03:54.960
"churn in the depth of the soul
of this river...called life."

00:03:57.418 --> 00:04:07.001
"When great mountains lay
in its path,"

00:04:08.918 --> 00:04:19.501
"it cuts deep gorges through
the rock...to keep flowing!.."

00:04:21.418 --> 00:04:38.376
"This unstoppable, inexhaustible
river called life..."

00:04:39.418 --> 00:04:45.626
"It is called
the river of life."

00:07:36.043 --> 00:07:37.501
Lord Shiva!

00:07:41.168 --> 00:07:43.001
For all the sins
I have committed,

00:07:43.168 --> 00:07:45.585
if death is the only redemption,
then take my life!...

00:07:45.793 --> 00:07:49.501
But this boy should live...

00:07:50.168 --> 00:07:54.668
He should live for his mother
who is waiting for him...

00:07:54.668 --> 00:07:57.876
he should live to ascend
the throne Mahishmati...

00:07:58.126 --> 00:08:01.626
Mahendra Baahubali should live!

00:08:34.626 --> 00:08:35.710
Dear me!

00:08:41.168 --> 00:08:43.251
Hey! What are you
waiting for? Hurry!

00:08:46.043 --> 00:08:47.626
Hey! Be careful!

00:09:12.668 --> 00:09:15.251
What happened?
- I am not sure, master.

00:09:15.543 --> 00:09:16.668
With all the jewelry on her,

00:09:16.668 --> 00:09:18.168
she must have been
a queen or something.

00:09:18.168 --> 00:09:20.460
She died with her
hand pointing up!

00:09:24.043 --> 00:09:25.126
Master!

00:09:28.293 --> 00:09:29.376
What happened?

00:09:29.376 --> 00:09:31.168
They must have come
here to kill her.

00:09:31.168 --> 00:09:33.751
Looks like she got
the better of them.

00:09:36.543 --> 00:09:37.626
Master!

00:09:41.668 --> 00:09:43.376
Oh my God! A cave!

00:09:43.376 --> 00:09:45.751
We never knew this existed!

00:09:47.876 --> 00:09:50.335
Looks like it goes all the way
to the top of the mountain!

00:09:50.751 --> 00:09:53.626
If the lady was holding the
baby up, pointing to the top,

00:09:53.793 --> 00:09:55.543
Maybe she wanted us
to take it back there!

00:09:55.543 --> 00:09:57.001
You are out of your mind?

00:09:57.251 --> 00:09:59.626
They sent soldiers
to kill an infant!

00:09:59.793 --> 00:10:01.001
What dangers do
you think await him...

00:10:01.001 --> 00:10:03.001
if you send him back there!
- But, Sanga..

00:10:04.543 --> 00:10:06.001
This is my baby.

00:10:06.668 --> 00:10:08.001
I have no children...

00:10:08.168 --> 00:10:09.876
and the river Goddess
has given this boy to me.

00:10:10.501 --> 00:10:15.001
If anyone of you object,
I will trample upon your necks.

00:10:15.293 --> 00:10:18.376
What are you waiting for?
Close the cave.

00:10:29.418 --> 00:10:30.501
Shiva!

00:10:34.168 --> 00:10:35.376
Shiva!

00:10:36.793 --> 00:10:38.501
What are you doing here,
my dear?

00:10:38.501 --> 00:10:40.335
What is up there, mother?

00:10:48.668 --> 00:10:50.793
There are ghosts
and demons up there!

00:10:50.793 --> 00:10:52.918
They prey on
and eat little kids!

00:10:52.918 --> 00:10:54.751
But I want to go up there,
mother!

00:10:54.918 --> 00:10:57.210
Don't ever say you want
to go up there! Let us go.

00:11:16.751 --> 00:11:19.251
How many times have I told you
not to climb up there?

00:11:19.251 --> 00:11:21.001
Why do you keep doing it?

00:11:21.001 --> 00:11:23.710
You are my darling, right?
You won't do it again, right?

00:12:16.001 --> 00:12:17.751
Looks like he will
make it this time.

00:12:17.751 --> 00:12:20.168
No way!
Look at the water mountain!

00:12:20.168 --> 00:12:21.626
It goes way up into the clouds...

00:12:21.793 --> 00:12:22.876
...And how many times has he fallen
from that hundred feet?

00:12:22.876 --> 00:12:23.751
He always slips and falls
after the first hundred feet.

00:12:23.918 --> 00:12:25.501
Yeah, he slipped and fell
at least a hundred times.

00:12:25.501 --> 00:12:28.251
Watch!
He is going to come sliding down again.

00:13:03.751 --> 00:13:05.501
Shiva!

00:13:05.501 --> 00:13:08.210
Your mother is upto something there!

00:13:09.168 --> 00:13:16.335
'Shiva, Shiva, Shiva, Shiva,
Shiva, Shiva, Shiva, Shiva!'

00:13:17.293 --> 00:13:18.626
That is fifteen!

00:13:18.918 --> 00:13:22.751
Pour another 101 times and
your prayers will be answered!

00:13:23.418 --> 00:13:27.001
Sage, if I do this,
will my son listen to me?

00:13:27.543 --> 00:13:29.251
Will he stop trying to climb
up that mountain?

00:13:29.418 --> 00:13:32.126
Of course!
This is a powerful ritual!

00:13:32.543 --> 00:13:35.126
Pour this water over Shiva,
with all your heart,

00:13:35.876 --> 00:13:38.626
and He will guide your son
onto the right path.

00:13:39.043 --> 00:13:40.876
Alright! 0! Sage.
- Hail Shiva!

00:13:41.793 --> 00:13:44.626
Mother, you are not
getting younger, are you?

00:13:45.376 --> 00:13:47.501
It won't help you if you
run around so much!

00:13:47.668 --> 00:13:50.001
Out of my way!
- Mother, please listen to me!

00:13:50.293 --> 00:13:52.501
Why should I?
Do you ever listen to me?

00:13:53.251 --> 00:13:55.376
Father, can you please
tell her to stop?

00:13:55.793 --> 00:13:57.376
Sanga?
- What?

00:13:57.793 --> 00:14:00.043
Where are the flowers?
- Father! Father!

00:14:00.043 --> 00:14:01.001
Let go of me!

00:14:01.251 --> 00:14:03.626
Alright! Let me do it on your behalf.
Okay?

00:14:03.918 --> 00:14:06.501
No way!
Lord Shiva won't accept it.

00:14:07.626 --> 00:14:10.126
The one who took the oath
will have to pour the water!

00:14:10.668 --> 00:14:13.626
Sire, carry on with what you are doing.
- Hail Lord Shiva!

00:14:14.418 --> 00:14:16.376
Mother.
- What is it now?

00:14:16.668 --> 00:14:18.751
How about I carry you...

00:14:18.918 --> 00:14:20.918
and you can pour the water
over Lord Shiva? Fine?

00:14:20.918 --> 00:14:23.251
No way!
Lord Shiva won't accept it.

00:14:23.251 --> 00:14:25.751
The one who took the oath
will have to pour the water

00:14:25.918 --> 00:14:27.876
and she has to walk up
to pour the water!

00:14:29.918 --> 00:14:33.626
Sage, are you and your Shiva
planning to kill my mother?

00:14:33.626 --> 00:14:37.001
How should I know what
the Lord has in store?

00:14:44.501 --> 00:14:45.626
Lord Shiva!

00:14:47.293 --> 00:14:48.668
Sanga!

00:14:48.668 --> 00:14:50.876
See what your lad is up to now!

00:14:51.293 --> 00:14:52.751
What is it this time?

00:14:58.793 --> 00:15:00.876
Shiva, stop!

00:15:01.876 --> 00:15:06.751
You will go to hell for this
blasphemy! Shiva, stop!

00:15:12.168 --> 00:15:13.376
Shiva.

00:15:30.876 --> 00:15:32.001
Shiva, wait..

00:15:34.043 --> 00:15:38.876
"The celestial river agitatedly
moving through His matted hair"

00:15:39.043 --> 00:15:44.126
"which makes His head shine
with those soft waves."

00:15:48.793 --> 00:15:53.751
"And His forehead shining
like a brilliant fire"

00:15:53.751 --> 00:15:56.001
"and the crescent of moon which
is an ornament to His head"

00:15:56.168 --> 00:15:59.335
"makes my mind love Him
each and every moment."

00:16:04.126 --> 00:16:08.585
"Who is he and
where he comes from?

00:16:09.001 --> 00:16:13.751
"He brought with him eternal
light spreading everywhere."

00:16:13.918 --> 00:16:18.251
"His strong arms can turn
the tide of history."

00:16:18.793 --> 00:16:22.043
"River Bhagirathi, Lord Shiva
head towards you."

00:16:22.043 --> 00:16:27.001
"Look at this great irony."

00:16:55.001 --> 00:16:59.876
"The consort of the sportive
daughter of the mountain"

00:16:59.876 --> 00:17:06.335
"whose mind rejoices
at Her side long glances."

00:17:07.168 --> 00:17:12.043
"With the stream of merciful
look which removes hardships"

00:17:12.043 --> 00:17:14.376
"Makes my mind
take pleasure in Him"

00:17:14.543 --> 00:17:18.085
"who wears the directions
as apparel."

00:17:19.376 --> 00:17:21.918
"With the lustrous gem"

00:17:21.918 --> 00:17:24.293
"on the serpent's hood
in His matted locks."

00:17:24.293 --> 00:17:26.626
"He, who is with His bride
whose face is decorated"

00:17:26.793 --> 00:17:30.001
"by the melting of
red saffron vermillion."

00:17:34.043 --> 00:17:36.543
"And who wears on His shoulder
the hide of the elephant"

00:17:36.543 --> 00:17:39.043
"which was blind
with ferociousness."

00:17:39.043 --> 00:17:41.418
"Makes my mind happy
and contented in Him"

00:17:41.418 --> 00:17:44.835
"who is the leader of demons."

00:18:04.626 --> 00:18:05.876
Mother!

00:18:06.168 --> 00:18:08.376
Not just a thousand
showers for your Lord,

00:18:08.793 --> 00:18:11.876
He will bathe all the time now.
Are you happy now?

00:18:14.168 --> 00:18:15.251
Yes..

00:19:13.918 --> 00:19:16.751
Sage, it played out
just like you predicted!

00:19:17.168 --> 00:19:21.501
My son hasn't looked up
at that waterfall since.

00:19:21.668 --> 00:19:24.501
Do you ever underestimate
Lord Shiva's power?

00:19:25.043 --> 00:19:28.376
But now he sits staring
at the wooden mask

00:19:28.793 --> 00:19:32.501
that fell on the Shivalingam
from above.

00:19:32.668 --> 00:19:33.960
Now what is with that?

00:19:35.418 --> 00:19:38.876
Lord Shiva works
in mysterious ways.

00:19:39.043 --> 00:19:40.501
Only He would know.

00:19:40.918 --> 00:19:41.668
A small doubt.

00:19:41.668 --> 00:19:43.751
Since my son was
the one who made sure

00:19:43.751 --> 00:19:45.335
the idol is bathed
all the time.

00:19:45.751 --> 00:19:48.001
Will his wish of climbing
up the mountain come true

00:19:48.168 --> 00:19:49.501
or will Sanga's
wish of him always

00:19:49.668 --> 00:19:50.793
staying down here come true?

00:19:50.793 --> 00:19:54.501
To hell with your doubts.
My son did what he did for me!

00:19:54.918 --> 00:19:57.751
My wish will be fulfilled.
Isn't that right?

00:19:58.501 --> 00:20:03.043
Lord Shiva does whatever
He thinks. Hail Lord Shiva!

00:20:03.043 --> 00:20:04.876
Hail Lord Shiva!

00:20:06.043 --> 00:20:06.751
What did he say?

00:20:13.918 --> 00:20:15.001
Shiva!

00:20:15.001 --> 00:20:17.293
How long are you going
to sit holding that wooden mask?

00:20:17.293 --> 00:20:19.626
There is somebody up there.

00:20:19.626 --> 00:20:22.251
Maybe there is, but your mother
is calling out to you.

00:20:22.418 --> 00:20:24.751
Let us go home.
- Go ahead. I will come later.

00:20:25.001 --> 00:20:26.251
Let us go, boys.

00:20:29.751 --> 00:20:33.085
Who are you?
Why did you come to me?

00:21:43.543 --> 00:21:48.251
"My heart is lost."

00:21:49.626 --> 00:21:55.376
"Like a drop in the waves."

00:21:55.793 --> 00:22:01.251
"I am the one whose
eyes shine amidst the stars"

00:22:02.001 --> 00:22:05.001
"I am the one who
sings amidst the waterfalls"

00:22:05.168 --> 00:22:09.876
"My voice echoes through
streams, listen to me!"

00:22:11.376 --> 00:22:16.335
"The persevering one, your
bravery will take you forward."

00:22:17.626 --> 00:22:22.501
"You leap higher and higher,
firm and stable and determined."

00:22:23.793 --> 00:22:28.751
"The persevering one, your
bravery will take you forward."

00:22:30.043 --> 00:22:35.751
"You leap higher and higher,
firm and stable and determined."

00:23:06.918 --> 00:23:08.751
"I breathe for you..."

00:23:10.001 --> 00:23:11.876
"and only you"

00:23:13.293 --> 00:23:18.751
"Come and let us live together."

00:23:19.376 --> 00:23:24.335
"Let me tell you something,
my love."

00:23:26.168 --> 00:23:31.751
"I chose you as my soul mate."

00:23:32.293 --> 00:23:38.626
"Whether I stumble and fall,
with haste I will come."

00:23:38.626 --> 00:23:43.001
"I am but a sudden gust of wind.
I stop for no one."

00:23:43.168 --> 00:23:51.126
"I will break free of every
mountain in no time."

00:23:51.126 --> 00:23:55.835
"He is strong and without an
equal adversary who can fight."

00:23:57.376 --> 00:24:02.085
"His anger will cause
new fears in his foes."

00:24:03.543 --> 00:24:08.251
"He is strong and without an
