(Sanskrit chants)

02:03:45.668 --> 02:03:51.001
(Sanskrit chants)

02:03:51.168 --> 02:03:56.376
(Sanskrit chants)

02:03:59.376 --> 02:04:02.376
Invincible!
- Invincible!

02:04:02.543 --> 02:04:05.251
Invincible!
- Invincible!

02:04:05.918 --> 02:04:08.126
Welcome, Baahubali!

